Package: squigit-stt
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: a7mddra <a7mddra@github.com>
Description: Standalone CLI STT engine for Squigit
 A headless, offline speech to text whisper-based engine designed for Squigit.
 No GUI overhead, pure CLI. Includes ggml-tiny.en.bin model.
